<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('meta')%>
        <%- include('style') %>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('header') %>
        <main class="main">

            <!-- ABOUT HERO -->
            <section class="about-hero">
                <div class="wrap about-hero-grid">
                    <div>
                        <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>
                        <h1>We got tired of<br>wiping in <em>circles.</em></h1>
                        <p class="lede">CLARO started on an optician's counter, not in a lab. We watched people wipe the
                            same haze in the same circles with the same cloth — and noticed the spray was always the
                            problem, not the person.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fog-panel">
                        <span class="fog-label top">Before CLARO</span>
                        <span class="fog-label bottom">After CLARO</span>
                        <span class="fog-caption">The same view, minus the film that alcohol sprays leave behind.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- ORIGIN TIMELINE -->
            <section class="origin">
                <div class="wrap">
                    <div class="section-head">
                        <span class="eyebrow">How We Got Here</span>
                        <h2 style="margin-top:14px;">From fitting counter to formula lab.</h2>
                        <p>Three real problems, in the order we solved them.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="clarity-track">
                        <div class="clarity-item">
                            <span class="haze">Problem 01</span>
                            <h3>Alcohol sprays were stripping AR coatings</h3>
                            <p>Opticians told us the "glass cleaner" from the drugstore was voiding coating warranties
                                within weeks. We started reformulating around a neutral pH base instead.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="clarity-item">
                            <span class="haze">Problem 02</span>
                            <h3>Ammonia cleaners left a haze of their own</h3>
                            <p>Great on windows, terrible on multicoated lenses — ammonia left a faint film that caught
                                the light under studio lamps. We cut it entirely.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="clarity-item">
                            <span class="haze">Problem 03</span>
                            <h3>Nothing dried fast enough for real use</h3>
                            <p>Photographers needed a formula that flashed off between shots. That became our benchmark:
                                under three seconds, every batch, every bottle.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- STATS -->
            <div class="stats-band">
                <div class="wrap" style="padding:56px 32px;">
                    <div class="stats-grid">
                        <div class="stat"><b>10,400+</b><span>Bottles shipped this year</span></div>
                        <div class="stat"><b>7.0</b><span>Neutral pH, every batch</span></div>
                        <div class="stat"><b>0%</b><span>Alcohol or ammonia</span></div>
                        <div class="stat"><b>3 sec</b><span>Average dry time</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- VALUES -->
            <section>
                <div class="wrap">
                    <div class="section-head">
                        <h2>What we won't compromise on</h2>
                        <p>The three rules every formula has to pass before it gets a bottle.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="values-grid">
                        <div class="value-card">
                            <div class="glyph">
                                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="var(--green-deep)" stroke-width="1.6" />
                                    <path d="M9 12L11 14L15 10" stroke="var(--green-deep)" stroke-width="1.6" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h4>Coating-safe, always</h4>
                            <p>Every formula is tested against AR, blue-light, and polarized coatings before it's
                                approved for bottling — no exceptions for a "stronger" batch.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="value-card">
                            <div class="glyph">
                                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                                    <path d="M12 2L20 6V12C20 17 16.5 20.7 12 22C7.5 20.7 4 17 4 12V6L12 2Z"
                                        stroke="var(--green-deep)" stroke-width="1.6" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h4>Plant-derived base</h4>
                            <p>No alcohol, no ammonia. Our surfactant base starts as a citrus derivative, which is tough
                                on oils without being harsh on coatings or skin.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="value-card">
                            <div class="glyph">
                                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                                    <path d="M3 12H21M12 3V21" stroke="var(--green-deep)" stroke-width="1.6"
                                        stroke-linecap="round" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h4>Tested where it's used</h4>
                            <p>Every batch is reviewed with the opticians and photographers who use it daily, not just
                                in a lab under ideal lighting.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- TEAM -->
            <section style="background:var(--bg-alt);">
                <div class="wrap">
                    <div class="section-head">
                        <h2>The people behind the bottle</h2>
                        <p>Small team, one formula, a lot of testing.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-grid">
                        <div class="team-card">
                            <div class="team-photo"><img
                                    src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3763188/pexels-photo-3763188.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=500"
                                    alt="Portrait of CLARO co-founder"></div>
                            <div class="team-body">
                                <h4>Renata Kobayashi</h4><span>Co-Founder, Chemistry</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-card">
                            <div class="team-photo"><img
                                    src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2379005/pexels-photo-2379005.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=500"
                                    alt="Portrait of CLARO co-founder"></div>
                            <div class="team-body">
                                <h4>Marcus Webb</h4><span>Co-Founder, Operations</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-card">
                            <div class="team-photo"><img
                                    src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3785079/pexels-photo-3785079.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=500"
                                    alt="Portrait of CLARO lab lead"></div>
                            <div class="team-body">
                                <h4>Priya Nair</h4><span>Formula Lab Lead</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-card">
                            <div class="team-photo"><img
                                    src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2955376/pexels-photo-2955376.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=500"
                                    alt="Portrait of CLARO customer care lead"></div>
                            <div class="team-body">
                                <h4>Owen Castillo</h4><span>Customer Care</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <section class="about-cta">
                <div class="wrap about-cta-inner">
                    <div>
                        <h2>Want to see the wipe test for yourself?</h2>
                        <p>Try CLARO on your own lenses, coated or not.</p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="index.html#shop" class="btn" style="background:var(--ink);color:var(--zing);">Shop the
                        Spray</a>
                </div>
            </section>

        </main>

        <%- include('footer') %>
            <%- include('js') %>
</body>

</html>